Package com.company

Class GameLogic

java.lang.Object
com.company.GameLogic
public class GameLogic extends Object
GameLogic class is responsible for processing data from the UI and making a decision afterwards. Data included is the fortress health, the number of tanks, a 2D array for the UI, a 2D cheat UI array, an array of tank identifiers, and a grid for game logic. The primary function of GameLogic is to generate tanks and manage the user's turn.
